items.title: Health insurers vow to speed approval of medical care
items.description: Some of the nation's health insurers say they're taking steps to speed the process by which doctors approve medical care.

items.title: U.S. embassy warns Americans in Qatar to shelter in place
items.description: "Out of an abundance of caution we recommend American citizens shelter in place until further notice," the U.S. Embassy in Doha, Qatar, said.

items.title: May 19: CBS News 24/7, 10am ET
items.description: Russia launches its largest drone attack on Ukraine; "60 Minutes" looks at how A.I. and autonomous weapons have changed face of modern war.

items.title: ICE detains Marine vet's wife who was still breastfeeding their baby
items.description: ICE officers detained the wife of a Marine Corps veteran in Louisiana during a routine immigration appointment.
